718448f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 65th Street
718448f-a.text:
North on Central Park West from 65th Street. The street is torn up for the construction of the Eighth Avenue subway. At the dat of this photograph, south bound traffic only was permitted on Central Park West. Now (1935) the reverse is true.
October 29, 1928.
P. L. Spenr, Photographer.
